# ğŸ§® 28. Find the Index of the First Occurrence in a String

ğŸ”— https://leetcode.com/problems/find-the-index-of-the-first-occurrence-in-a-string/description/?envType=problem-list-v2&envId=eeudwo2i

## âœ… Approach:
used nested loop and two pointers to iterate through haystack to find the occurence of needle
used a flag variable to check the loop didt break and satisfied the conditon

## â±ï¸ Time Complexity:
- O(N1 X N2) time, O(1) space

## ğŸ”¤ Code (Java):
```java
class Solution {
    public int strStr(String haystack, String needle) {
        int l=0;
        int N1=haystack.length();
        int N2=needle.length();
        while(l<=(N1-N2)){
            int flag=1;
            for(int i=0;i<N2;i++){
                if(haystack.charAt(l+i)!=needle.charAt(i)){
                    flag=0;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if(flag==1){
                return l;
            }
            l++;
        }
        return -1;
    }
}
